data.description: Location Location Location!! Located on a quiet cul-de-sac it's private and fully fenced with private electric gates. This home boasts a large 60x40 shop with 2 floors this shop is perfect for storing all of your equipment and vehicles. Plus a second 2.5 car large garage! This property has 2, 400AMP panels. In a separate building, you'll find a spacious 480-square-foot attached bonus room that can be used as a home gym, game room, or additional living space. The patio, huge deck, and back porch provide plenty of room for outdoor entertaining and relaxation. But that's not all - this home also offers lots of storage space, ensuring that you'll have plenty of room for all of your belongings. Don't miss out on this incredible opportunity to own a home with all of the features you've been looking for.
